Minimum insurance - 4.5<0xE2><0x88><0x92>5 thousand rubles (about 1100<0xE2><0x88><0x92>1300 hryvnia).
Those who go nearby (say, to Georgia, Armenia) with cargo worth up to 50 thousand dollars, pay somewhere 15 thousand rubles (3800 hryvnias) and pass.
