Conditions for survival at the border - none, - complain truckers, settled to eat near their cars.
In border shops and cafes and so always expensive, but such prices as here, we have not met anywhere!
The sellers oriented and quickly rolled them up: 15 hryvnias is a bar, seven hryvnias - a cup of coffee, 25 hryvnias - a plate of soup.
